---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

export const metadata = {
  school: "Discipleship Bible School",
  location: "Sendai, Japan",
  method: "Inductive Bible Study",
  curriculum: "Genesis to Revelation, Historical Context, Worldview",
};
---

<Layout title="Discipleship Bible School | YWAM Sendai">
  <main class="bg-dark-bg min-h-screen text-zinc-300 pb-20">
    
    <div class="h-[45vh] relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/hero-sendai.jpg" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20" />
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <a href="/en" class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] text-gold-accent hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity uppercase mb-4 block">← Back to Home</a>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif text-white">DBS</h1>
        <p class="tracking-[.2em] uppercase text-xs mt-2">Discipleship Bible School</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-12 space-y-20">
      
      <section class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-white italic">One Story. 66 Books. 12 Weeks.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
          The DBS is a three-month immersion into the sacred scriptures. Moving chronologically from Genesis to Revelation, you will discover the Bible not as a collection of fragmented verses, but as a <span class="text-white">unified narrative</span> of God’s redemptive work. In our Sendai community, we approach the Word with both the heart of a contemplative and the mind of a scholar.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl">
          <h4 class="text-gold-accent text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">01. Observation</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-500 italic">"What does the text say?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl">
          <h4 class="text-gold-accent text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">02. Interpretation</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-500 italic">"What did it mean then?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl">
          <h4 class="text-gold-accent text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">03. Application</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-500 italic">"How do we walk it now?"</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-[2.5rem]">
          <h3 class="text-gold-accent font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] mb-4">The Journey</h3>
          <h4 class="text-xl text-white font-serif mb-4 italic">Chronological Reading</h4>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            Read through all 66 books in the order they occurred. Understand the historical context of the prophets, the cultural weight of the Law, and the explosive birth of the early Church.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-[2.5rem]">
          <h3 class="text-gold-accent font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] mb-4">The Context</h3>
          <h4 class="text-xl text-white font-serif mb-4 italic">Small Group Tables</h4>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            Scripture was meant to be read in community. Our "Table" culture allows you to process the week’s reading with others, identifying how the Biblical worldview challenges and aligns our own.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-zinc-900/20 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl text-center">
            <span class="block text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-600 mb-2 tracking-widest">Next Start</span>
            <span class="text-zinc-200 font-bold text-sm">Apr 2027</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900/20 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl text-center">
            <span class="block text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-600 mb-2 tracking-widest">Duration</span>
            <span class="text-zinc-200 font-bold text-sm">12 Weeks</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900/20 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl text-center">
            <span class="block text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-600 mb-2 tracking-widest">Base Cost</span>
            <span class="text-zinc-200 font-bold text-sm">¥420,000*</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900/20 border border-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-3xl text-center border-gold-accent/30">
            <span class="block text-[9px] uppercase text-gold-accent mb-2 tracking-widest">Combo Discount</span>
            <span class="text-gold-accent font-bold text-sm">-¥50,000</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
        
        <div class="bg-gold-accent/5 border border-gold-accent/20 p-6 rounded-3xl text-center">
          <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed italic">
            *Includes tuition & accommodation.<br/>
            For a full breakdown of costs, including food and travel budgets, <a href="https://guide.ywamsendai.org/en/roles/students/school-costs/" class="text-gold-accent underline">visit the Guide</a>.<br/>
            Students who complete the Sendai DTS in the same year receive the ¥50,000 "Combo Discount" on their DBS tuition.
          </p>
        </div>

      <div class="text-center py-10 border-t border-zinc-900">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-white mb-8 italic">Deepen your roots in the Word.</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
          <button class="open-hub-trigger inline-block px-12 py-5 bg-zinc-100 text-black font-black rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-white/5">
            Connect & Apply
          </button>
          <p class="text-[10px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
            Prerequisite: Successful completion of a DTS
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>